nodes.text: In 20 ABY, this individual worked at the Reflection Gardens on Coruscant. A Human woman, she spotted two suspicious looking men (Imperial commandos Chik Apla and Chala Venan) among the trees several days before the Wedding of Luke Skywalker and Mara Jade. She asked what they were doing in the Gardens, and was told they were spraying for Garqi vert-mites.
